%p Hi!
%p
  A ticket for the project
  = "\"#{@ticket.project.name}\", "
  created by
  = @ticket.user.name + ", "
  has been assigned to you.
    
%p 
  Ticket info:
  %br/
  = @ticket.name

%blockquote
  = simple_format(@ticket.description)
  
  
%p
  The ticket has the urgency of:
  = @ticket.urgency_line

%p
  To see further information on the issue, please visit the ticket via the 
  = link_to 'online support system.', @ticket
  
